{"tid":1617041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"平日晚間開花好似好有效","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:35:03.000Z","uid":80529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bdbac03c509bec6965bfa7869d219abee76d51","tid":1617041,"uid":80529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"比起大型陣地戰，損兵嘅程度較少（雖然都有居民流血同巴打被拉...)<br />\n但係對狗黎講，平日同你玩番幾個鐘<br />\n都咪話唔攰唔燥，啲狗都好似再癲啲咁<br />\n二黎，觀感好似比日間為好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三，居民嘅參與率多過日間，用力屌埋一份<br />\n當然當中都有缺點嘅，但整體上夜晚幾區開花<br />\n個影響程度都幾可觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce851d4978a694fb7f7d76982b2f0c0675bbd7f1","tid":1617041,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"聽日早上九點半 沙田裁判法院聲援義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}